><strong>Subscription:</strong> Any active subscriptions will be forfeit.</li><li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> It may take up to 30 days to fully remove all associated data.</li></ul><p>By confirming, you acknowledge that you have read and understood these terms.</p>','Account Deletion Policy','Chính sách Xóa tài khoản','Account Deletion Policy','DELETE_ACCOUNT','2026-04-04 09:30:35.816508','2026-04-04 09:30:35.816508');
